        },
        {
            "text": "of exotic charmonium-like states. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "A new, 2.5 m long liquid hydrogen target (\u223c0.27X 0 ) is much more transparent for photons than the 6 LiD and NH 3 targets that were used before. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "The target is surrounded by a 4 m long recoil proton detector which can be used to reconstruct and identify recoil protons via time-of-flight and energy loss measurements. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "The existing system of two electromagnetic calorimeters is extended by installation of the new large-aperture calorimeter. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "With the new calorimetry system one can expect much better selection of exclusive events.",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "Searching for production of exotic charmonia that decay into final states with photons like Z 0 (3900) \u2192 J/\u03c8\u03c0 0 , X(3872) \u2192 J/\u03c8\u03c9, X(3872) \u2192 J/\u03c8\u03b7 etc. will be possible with the upgraded setup. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "The final states decaying to the \u03c7 c0,1,2 -mesons could also be studied.",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "New results on photoproduction of exotic charmonia could be expected from the LHC experiments where sizeable statistics of J/\u03c8, comparable with one available at COMPASS, produced in ultra-peripheral hadronic collisions is collected [15,16,17,18]. ",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 3,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 232,
                    "end": 236,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b13",
                    "text": "[15,"
                },
                {
                    "start": 236,
