                    "id": "software-simple-s4"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "The Electron-Ion Collider [19] presently being discussed could also be an important source of new information about photoproduction of exotic charmonia.",
            "section": "Exclusive muoproduction of X(3872)",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 3,
