        },
        {
            "text": "Conclusions",
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "Lepto(photo-)production of exotic charmonia is a new direction in physics of the XYZ states started by COMPASS. ",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
            "section_rank": 4,
            "entity_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 103,
                    "end": 110,
                    "type": "software",
                    "rawForm": "COMPASS",
                    "resp": "service",
                    "id": "software-simple-s5"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "A new state X(3872) was observed with the statistical significance of 4.1\u03c3 in the exclusive charge-exchange reaction \u00b5 + N \u2192 \u00b5 + N (J/\u03c8\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 )\u03c0 \u00b1 . ",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "Its mass M X(3872) = 3860.0 \u00b1 10.4 MeV/c 2 , width \u0393 X(3872) < 51 and the decay mode X(3872) \u2192 J/\u03c8\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 are consistent with the X(3872). ",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "But the observed two-pion mass spectrum shows disagreement with previous experimental results for the X(3872). ",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "A possible explanation could be that the observed state X(3872) is the C = 1 partner of the X(3872) as predicted by a tetraquark model. ",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "Estimated rates of photoproduction of exotic charmonia obtained by COMPASS or based on COMPASS results are summarized in Fig. 4  [6,14,12].",
            "section": "Conclusions",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
